text: Marian Jade Saldajeno Capadocia (born September 17, 1995) is a tennis player from the Philippines. She began playing tennis at the age of 8 and started her professional career at the age of 15. Born in Manila, she reached her highest individual ranking in the Philippines in 2011, when she became number one.
